(820, 194, 'td_wp_editor', 'Focused on inspiring youth for converging them toward a better world through our steadfast portal with strong content matter such as crazy listed articles, images &amp; entertaining videos with an aim to attract &amp; connect with audience worldwide.  Liberty free flow of information with an honest approach to support the event and fight against the odds. Our major concern is to combat back with the power of non-censored words to improve the worsening social situation decaying our country. Befitting reply content for every news turning viral with a sugar rush and converting it into a crazy information which will be viral with the support of our wild followers.\r\n\r\nWe are not too serious people so take us lightly and welcome us with a warm heart and from our part we solemnly swear to all the almighty that we will keep you in a stress-free spirit with some irrational &amp; rational information roaring loud on the world. Whether it is entertainment, music, sport, love &amp; sex, fiction, art, culture, funny jargons, etc. we will bring you everything that we will make you continue with us as our sensible followers. Our finishing touch to every content matter will be a sure shot bolt from the blue bombshell which will burst like a nuclear weapon &amp; sound like a blast with some nuisance sound effect.'),
