(176, 2, '2016-11-20 07:30:45', '2016-11-20 07:30:45', 'In the outskirts of Kanpur, the time was around 3:00am soon the sun was preparing to come out with brightness, but everything shattered when Patna- Indore Express got derailed along with his 14 coaches. At least, 96 people are assumed to be dead and the rescue operation is being carried with full support of the government and many people\'s are still trapped inside fighting for life with a light of hope.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_179\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"288\"]<a href=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/shocking-tragedy-kanpur-patna-express-death-tolls-increases-96-150-injured/capture111/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-179\"><img class=\" wp-image-179\" src=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Capture111-300x220.png\" alt=\"Pics from the incident\" width=\"288\" height=\"211\" /></a> Pics from the incident[/caption]\r\n\r\nMore than 150 people have been injured and the numbers may rise till the end of properly executed rescue process.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/shocking-tragedy-kanpur-patna-express-death-tolls-increases-96-150-injured/indbpatnaa-1/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-180\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-180\" src=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/indbpatnaa-1-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"indbpatnaa-1\" width=\"727\" height=\"545\" /></a>\r\n\r\nActual reasons are still unknown, because everybody is in grief.\r\n\r\nNorthern Indian Railway is tyring to work with full pledged responsibility and have issued various helpline numbers to reduce the increasing grief due to this shocking incident.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_177\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"207\"]<a href=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/shocking-tragedy-kanpur-patna-express-death-tolls-increases-96-150-injured/capture/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-177\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-177\" src=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Capture-207x300.png\" alt=\"helpline NUMBERS\" width=\"207\" height=\"300\" /></a> helpline NUMBERS[/caption]\r\n\r\nWho will be held responsible for the lives of innocent?\r\n\r\nMay God give strength to their family!!!! RIP INNOCENT SOULS.............\r\n\r\nhERE HOW CM Akhilesh Yadav tweeted with the list of helpline numbers-\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_181\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"872\"]<a href=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/shocking-tragedy-kanpur-patna-express-death-tolls-increases-96-150-injured/capture121/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-181\"><img class=\"wp-image-181\" src=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Capture121-300x174.png\" alt=\"Northern Railway helpline\" width=\"872\" height=\"506\" /></a> Northern Railway helpline[/caption]\r\n\r\n# All the Howrah, Mumbai rail routes have been disrupted due to such a grief-stricken incident.\r\n\r\nPM Modi has announced with his sorrowful soul- 2 lakhs to the family of dead &amp; 50,000 to the family of injured people in the shocking incident.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_185\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"482\"]<a href=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/shocking-tragedy-kanpur-patna-express-death-tolls-increases-96-150-injured/narendra-modi_650x400_81479022071/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-185\"><img class=\" wp-image-185\" src=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/narendra-modi_650x400_81479022071-300x185.jpg\" alt=\"Narendra Modi\" width=\"482\" height=\"297\" /></a> Narendra Modi[/caption]\r\n\r\nAll the local village people are working hand in hand with the railway employees to save as much life they can. Many people are fighting back with injuries and they are getting transferred to the government hospitals for treatment, so that lives their lives can be saved with NO loss of life.\r\n\r\nSuresh Prabhu will be reaching the incident place soon to monitor all the operations effectively and will try to know the loopholes which resulted in such a disastrous situation which has cost much precious life.\r\n\r\nSo, pray to all your almighty so that the worsening tragedy gets recovered soon.\r\n\r\nEvery year I noticed this type of Train crashes, which costs 100 of lives, it\'s clear now that we have a lot of shortfalls in our Indian Railway System.\r\n\r\nHow to stop these tragedies from happening next time?\r\n\r\nThis is influential concern.....May be soon we will know the drawbacks due to which this crash occurred. Only middle class &amp; poor class suffers the most because maximum of our exploding population come under middle range of per capital income and others with low per capital who travel the most in trains nowadays.', 'Shocking tragedy in Kanpur- Patna Express , death tolls increases to 96 more than 150 injured', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shocking-tragedy-kanpur-patna-express-death-tolls-increases-96-150-injured', '', '', '2016-11-20 13:16:33', '2016-11-20 13:16:33', '', 0, 'http://www.maikalaal.com/?p=176', 0, 'post', '', 0),
