(229, 1, '2016-11-21 16:26:12', '2016-11-21 16:26:12', '8 IAF Jets landed for the first touch in Agra- Lucknow Expressway.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Akhilesh_Yadav\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Akhilesh Yadav</strong></a>, CM of Uttar Pradesh, accomplished his promise before elections, maybe we can think this as a strategy to win elections, but who cares when India is developing its states smartly. Agra- Lucknow Expressway WAS INAUGURATED IN THE PRESENCE OF Samajwadi Party chief <strong>Mulayam Singh Yadav</strong> along with the party members and the common mob. Akhilesh Yadav is a young spirit, no doubt, he is keeping his promise of flourishing the state with a hope of development.\r\n<h2>Developing India-Fastest Highways</h2>\r\nOur IAF pilots showed their high-flying wings in the air with pride on an event where history has been created of constructs India’s largest 302 km long highway, which will rally around people a lot in saving time from long  queues of traffic. It was a grand opening ceremony where Akhilesh Yadav waved the flag of its biggest accomplishment as a sturdy Chief Minister of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uttar_Pradesh\" target=\"_blank\">Uttar Pradesh</a>.\r\n\r\nIt was projected as a dream project of the Samajwadi Party and without suspicion it’s true. The expense utilized was 13,200 Crore and has left a no goodbye mark for it\'s recorded completion time of <strong>22 months</strong>.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_230\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"640\"]<img class=\"wp-image-230 size-large\" src=\"http://www.maikalaal.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/NH-2-prepared-for-more-good-things-Emergency-landing-roads-1024x576.png\" alt=\"NH2 prepared for more good things Emergency landing on the roads\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /> NH-2-prepared-for-more-good-things-Emergency-landing-roads[/caption]\r\n\r\n<strong>Uttar Pradesh Expressway Industrial Development Authority</strong> (UPEIDA) played a vital role in executing this project successfully and this organization made an Extra mile of road to trouble free land the<strong> 8 IAF Sukhoi</strong> Jets.\r\n\r\nThis project was inaugurated with our patriotic Air Force to demonstrate the whole world how this Expressway will be useful in a war like emergencies. A few months back, a supersonic French Military, Military aircraft landed on the Mathura road. Yamuna Expressway, which has been a blessing so far for the nation.\r\n\r\nAgra- Lucknow Expressway will  enormously reduce the time hassle of the Indian citizens, by cutting down the traveling time between Agra to Lucknow with more than 65 % which has been tested by the UP dedicated government Organization.\r\n\r\nHats Off to Chief Minister, Akhilesh Yadav, who proved that the young politician souls can deliver better than the one who speaks better &amp; delivers less. This can be a political agenda of SP to gain votes in the upcoming elections, and the other political parties are also scared by the fact that citizens are blissfully supporting this project for the reason that the traffic nuisance in Lucknow &amp; Agra will drop down to a much bigger extent.\r\n\r\n<strong>Some poor political souls are imagining their defeat in the forthcoming election game. I am calling this a game or sport because I can witness some strong on-field practice by the election players.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Indian Highways - Connecting nation from road', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'indian-highways-connecting-nation-road', '', '', '2016-11-21 16:26:12', '2016-11-21 16:26:12', '', 0, 'http://www.maikalaal.com/?p=229', 0, 'post', '', 0),
