(320, 5, '2016-12-03 19:08:06', '2016-12-03 19:08:06', '<h2>ONE MAN ARMY</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLook like something fishy with so called “<a href=\"https://www.google.co.in/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=9&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiTx7mH2tjQAhXJMY8KHf3DBHwQFghFMAg&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAam_Aadmi_Party&amp;usg=AFQjCNEQFFfCe1N92P3HyIeEi_yHMIZGgw&amp;sig2=6sgvjSePrmdYx4K9BXDI8w\" target=\"_blank\">Aam Aadmi Party” (AAP)</a> the guy <a href=\"https://www.google.co.in/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=10&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjwlqqZ2tjQAhVLOY8KHU_7Cu8QFgg_MAk&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FArvind_Kejriwal&amp;usg=AFQjCNHpzMVLXLPV_dmpfrKauVdDohzELg&amp;sig2=jgOSH_rx1n1I1iyN2ji_vw\" target=\"_blank\">Arvind Kejriwal</a> with awesome knowledge of everything wasting his time in criticising opposition party (BJP, CONGRSS etc).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<h2>What’s wrong with him</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHe tries to fix all problems of India all alone which is not possible any how or if we think in the different manner may be he is the big fan of HITLER and want to become Junior Hitler of India.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<h2>Some Good points in Kejriwal</h2>\r\n<strong>The </strong>group of dedicated and young guys maximum youth participating in it working very hard in the progress of nation and trying to build good nation altogether, but if we go inside the party everyone is so confused what to do.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<h2>The basic flaws</h2>\r\nThey called themselves as “<strong>AAM aadmi ki party</strong>” but if you go inside them rarely you will find any <strong>AAM aadmi </strong>among them they are just like other corrupted party but, they have better way to collect money from the people as being the IIT’ians political party only this is the bloody difference.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<h2>Change the Culture</h2>\r\n<strong> As </strong>we learn from the starting TEAM work is the key of success so, why we cannot create TEAM in Indian political culture so that India can grow well as one nation why they waste their time in blaming each other and wasting their time also many people follow them which results in nothing.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<h2>My Simple Question</h2>\r\nWhy cannot all good minds from all the political party work together to make India a better place to live? This will close the culture of blame game on each other and they can focus on the work instead of big talks.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Arvind Kejriwal should stop blaming others if he finds anybody doing cheating from the nation or any other thing he must file case in court instead of coming in front of media and speaking with his “MUFLLAR and KHASI” this will be beneficial for the Kejriwal ji too nobody can accuse him.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<h2>Inclusion and request to all so called parties of India</h2>\r\nIf any party or minister is doing good for the nation let him do the things and also support him to do better weather its MODI Ji “MAKE IN INDIA” or something of Kjeriwal and yes one final and most important thing, all the Netaji’s of India request you has already earned lot of money from the common people lets give them some work so that their kid can do great things to make India proud.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Pollution</strong>: - It is one of the most dangerous issue for the nation all parties must work together to make India blissful place to live.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Education System:</strong> - Lets create as many as good schools in India so that children’s roaming around us can take education from their and ignite their minds to do awesome things.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Girl Care</strong>: - They are better than boys in all fields weather its education, taking care of anybody, can tolerate more than boys and last but not