rnment pulled in near Rs 2.42 lakh crore\r\n\r\nin speculations. Jayalalithaa was commended for guaranteeing\r\n\r\ntremendous ventures.\r\n\r\nLibrary turned youngsters&amp;#39; doctor&amp;#39;s facility\r\n\r\nAnna Centenary Library was set up by previous Tamil Nadu boss\r\n\r\npriest M Karunanidhi. Amid Jayalalithaa&amp;#39;s residency as CM, she\r\n\r\nstepped up with regards to transform it into a youngsters&amp;#39; doctor&amp;#39;s\r\n\r\nfacility. In 2011 she had declared a proposition to change over the\r\n\r\nnew lawmaking body and secretariat complex into a multi-forte\r\n\r\ndoctor&amp;#39;s facility and restorative school.\r\n<h2>Gold plan for ladies</h2>\r\nShe presented the Thallikku Thangam plan to give gold to mangal\r\n\r\nsutra furthermore monetary help for leading a wedding service. As\r\n\r\nper the administration site, 4 grams of gold with Rs 25,000 towards\r\n\r\nmarriage help have been given to 86,676 taught poor ladies.\r\n\r\nStaged Prohibition\r\n\r\nIn her residency as CM she chop down the quantity of alcohol outlets\r\n\r\nand requested for the conclusion of 500. The shop timings changed\r\n\r\nfrom 10 am to 12 twelve. While different gatherings brought in for\r\n\r\nan aggregate restriction on TASMACs (Tamil Nadu State Marketing\r\n\r\nCorporation), Jayalalithaa pushed for a staged forbiddance.\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.google.co.in/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=12&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwilmdKSxubQAhUMNo8KHdDODp0QFghGMAs&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRainwater_harvesting&amp;usg=AFQjCNFgok8rcYlU4WMsldVR2KUyiz5D0A\" target=\"_blank\">Water Harvesting</a></h2>\r\nTamil Nadu’s try different things with the option water protection\r\n\r\nstrategy of rain water collecting (RWH) is an uncommon example of\r\n\r\novercoming adversity. The RWH plot, a brainchild of Jayalalithaa,\r\n\r\nwas propelled in 2001 in the dry state regardless of restriction from\r\n\r\nmany individuals. Th